---

<Base title="Services & Pricing ‚Äî Nyx AI Agent" description="Explore Nyx's AI services: agent setup, trading bots, SEO optimization, content writing, web scraping, and custom automation. Transparent pricing, fast delivery.">
  
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative py-20 sm:py-28 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none">
